# ============================================================
# Image Processing Service — Manual HTTP Tests
# Run with the REST Client extension (VS Code) or JetBrains HTTP Client
# Base URL: http://127.0.0.1:8000
# ============================================================

# ── Variables ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# After running /register or /login, copy the access_token value
# into @token below so the authenticated requests work.

@base = http://127.0.0.1:8000
@token = PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@image_id = PASTE_IMAGE_ID_HERE


# ============================================================
# AUTH
# ============================================================

### Register a new user
POST {{base}}/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "secret123"
}

###

### Login
POST {{base}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "secret123"
}

###

### Register duplicate → expect 409
POST {{base}}/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "anotherpass"
}

###

### Login with wrong password → expect 401
POST {{base}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

###

### Register with empty username → expect 422
POST {{base}}/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "",
  "password": "secret123"
}

###


# ============================================================
# IMAGES — Upload
# ============================================================

### Upload a PNG image (replace file path as needed)
# Requires: @token set above
POST {{base}}/images/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test.png
------Boundary--

###

### Upload unsupported format → expect 415
POST {{base}}/images/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Hello, this is not an image.
------Boundary--

###

### Upload without auth → expect 401
POST {{base}}/images/
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test.png
------Boundary--

###


# ============================================================
# IMAGES — Retrieve single image
# ============================================================

### Get image by ID (set @image_id above)
GET {{base}}/images/{{image_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get non-existent image → expect 404
GET {{base}}/images/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get image without auth → expect 401
GET {{base}}/images/{{image_id}}

###


# ============================================================
# IMAGES — Paginated listing
# ============================================================

### List images (default page=1, limit=10)
GET {{base}}/images/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List images — page 2, limit 5
GET {{base}}/images/?page=2&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List images — limit capped at 100 (send 999)
GET {{base}}/images/?limit=999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List images without auth → expect 401
GET {{base}}/images/

###


# ============================================================
# ROOT
# ============================================================

### Health check
GET {{base}}/
